msgid ""
"While wearing this armor, you gain a +1 bonus to AC, and you can understand "
"and speak Abyssal. In addition, the armor's clawed gauntlets turn unarmed "
"strikes with your hands into magic weapons that deal slashing damage, with a "
"+1 bonus to attack rolls and damage rolls and a damage die of 1d8.    \n"
"**Curse.** Once you don this cursed armor, you can't doff it unless you are "
"targeted by the **_remove curse_** spell or similar magic. While wearing the "
"armor, you have disadvantage on attack rolls against demons and on saving "
"throws against their spells and special abilities. \n"
msgstr ""
